Package org.linuxforhealth.fhir.ecqm.common

This package provides model-independent classes for evaluating FHIR clinical quality measures. This code was ported from the cql-evaluator/evaluator.measure module and adapted to remove an unnecessary dependency on the HAPI FHIR model and to support supplemental data elements as seen in the cqf-ruler project.
